{
  "video_id": "gIbIewxHQrk",
  "title": "Saki Mafundikwa: Ingenuity and elegance in ancient African alphabets",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12802.0,
      "end_time": 16553.0,
      "text": "I moved back home 15 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16577.0,
      "end_time": 19417.0,
      "text": "after a 20-year stay in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19441.0,
      "end_time": 21781.0,
      "text": "and Africa called me back."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21805.0,
      "end_time": 25322.0,
      "text": "And I founded my country&#39;s first"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25346.0,
      "end_time": 27633.0,
      "text": "graphic design and new media college."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27657.0,
      "end_time": 32558.0,
      "text": "And I called it the Zimbabwe Institute of Vigital Arts."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32583.0,
      "end_time": 36796.0,
      "text": "The idea, the dream, was really for a sort of Bauhaus"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36820.0,
      "end_time": 41402.0,
      "text": "sort of school where new ideas were interrogated"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41426.0,
      "end_time": 44615.0,
      "text": "and investigated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44639.0,
      "end_time": 47375.0,
      "text": "the creation of a new visual language"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47399.0,
      "end_time": 52356.0,
      "text": "based on the African creative heritage."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 52380.0,
      "end_time": 55781.0,
      "text": "We offer a two-year diploma"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55805.0,
      "end_time": 59545.0,
      "text": "to talented students who have successfully completed"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59569.0,
      "end_time": 61725.0,
      "text": "their high school education."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61749.0,
      "end_time": 64662.0,
      "text": "And typography&#39;s a very important part of the curriculum"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 64686.00000000001,
      "end_time": 69605.0,
      "text": "and we encourage our students to look inward for influence."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 69629.0,
      "end_time": 71971.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a poster designed by one of the students"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 71995.0,
      "end_time": 76128.0,
      "text": "under the theme \"Education is a right.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76152.0,
      "end_time": 80411.0,
      "text": "Some logos designed by my students."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 80435.0,
      "end_time": 84479.0,
      "text": "Africa has had a long tradition of writing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 84503.0,
      "end_time": 86651.0,
      "text": "but this is not such a well-known fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 86675.0,
      "end_time": 90584.0,
      "text": "and I wrote the book \"Afrikan Alphabets\" to address that."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 90608.0,
      "end_time": 94131.0,
      "text": "The different types of writing in Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 94155.0,
      "end_time": 96376.0,
      "text": "first was proto-writing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 96400.0,
      "end_time": 98544.0,
      "text": "as illustrated by Nsibidi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98568.0,
      "end_time": 101616.0,
      "text": "which is the writing system of a secret society"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101640.0,
      "end_time": 105446.0,
      "text": "of the Ejagham people in southern Nigeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 105470.0,
      "end_time": 109316.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a special-interest writing system."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 109340.0,
      "end_time": 112891.0,
      "text": "The Akan of people of Ghana and [Cote d&#39;Ivoire]"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 112915.0,
      "end_time": 116936.0,
      "text": "developed Adinkra symbols some 400 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 116960.0,
      "end_time": 120803.0,
      "text": "and these are proverbs, historical sayings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 120828.0,
      "end_time": 123514.0,
      "text": "objects, animals, plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 123538.0,
      "end_time": 125521.0,
      "text": "and my favorite Adinkra system"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 125546.0,
      "end_time": 127898.0,
      "text": "is the first one at the top on the left."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 127922.0,
      "end_time": 128900.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called Sankofa."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 128924.0,
      "end_time": 134894.0,
      "text": "It means, \"Return and get it.\" Learn from the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 134918.0,
      "end_time": 137695.0,
      "text": "This pictograph by the Jokwe people of Angola"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 137719.0,
      "end_time": 141513.0,
      "text": "tells the story of the creation of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 141538.0,
      "end_time": 146918.0,
      "text": "At the top is God, at the bottom is man, mankind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 146942.0,
      "end_time": 151826.0,
      "text": "and on the left is the sun, on the right is the moon."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 151850.0,
      "end_time": 155680.0,
      "text": "All the paths lead to and from God."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 155705.0,
      "end_time": 160750.0,
      "text": "These secret societies of the Yoruba, Kongo"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 160990.0,
      "end_time": 162269.0,
      "text": "and Palo religions"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 162294.0,
      "end_time": 166700.0,
      "text": "in Nigeria, Congo and Angola respectively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 166310.0,
      "end_time": 169931.0,
      "text": "developed this intricate writing system"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 169955.0,
      "end_time": 173700.0,
      "text": "which is alive and well today in the New World"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 173724.0,
      "end_time": 179887.0,
      "text": "in Cuba, Brazil and Trinidad and Haiti."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 179912.0,
      "end_time": 183184.0,
      "text": "In the rainforests of the Democratic Republic of Congo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 183208.0,
      "end_time": 186750.0,
      "text": "in the Ituri society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 186990.0,
      "end_time": 189846.0,
      "text": "the men pound out a cloth out of a special tree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 189870.0,
      "end_time": 192939.0,
      "text": "and the women, who are also the praise singers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 192963.0,
      "end_time": 195620.0,
      "text": "paint interweaving patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 195644.0,
      "end_time": 198350.0,
      "text": "that are the same in structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 198374.0,
      "end_time": 203500.0,
      "text": "as the polyphonic structures that they use in their singing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 203290.0,
      "end_time": 206993.0,
      "text": "a sort of a musical score, if you may."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 207170.0,
      "end_time": 209742.0,
      "text": "In South Africa, Ndebele women"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 209766.0,
      "end_time": 213100.0,
      "text": "use these symbols and other geometric patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 213124.0,
      "end_time": 216914.0,
      "text": "to paint their homes in bright colors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 216938.0,
      "end_time": 219835.0,
      "text": "and the Zulu women use the symbols"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 219860.0,
      "end_time": 221334.0,
      "text": "in the beads that they weave"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 221358.0,
      "end_time": 224477.0,
      "text": "into bracelets and necklaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 224501.0,
      "end_time": 228556.0,
      "text": "Ethiopia has had the longest tradition of writing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 228580.0,
      "end_time": 230875.0,
      "text": "with the Ethiopic script that was developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 230899.0,
      "end_time": 232837.0,
      "text": "in the fourth century A.D."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 232861.0,
      "end_time": 235351.0,
      "text": "and is used to write Amharic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 235375.0,
      "end_time": 238636.0,
      "text": "which is spoken by over 24 million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 238660.0,
      "end_time": 243930.0,
      "text": "King Ibrahim Njoya of the Bamum Kingdom of Cameroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 243117.0,
      "end_time": 246658.0,
      "text": "developed Shü-mom at the age of 25."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 246682.0,
      "end_time": 248744.0,
      "text": "Shü-mom is a writing system."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 248769.0,
      "end_time": 251738.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a syllabary. It&#39;s not exactly an alphabet."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 251762.0,
      "end_time": 255530.0,
      "text": "And here we see three stages of development"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 255770.0,
      "end_time": 259692.0,
      "text": "that it went through in 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 259716.0,
      "end_time": 265252.0,
      "text": "The Vai people of Liberia had a long tradition of literacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 265276.0,
      "end_time": 269187.0,
      "text": "before their first contact with Europeans in the 1800s."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 269211.0,
      "end_time": 273769.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a syllabary and reads from left to right."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 273793.0,
      "end_time": 277340.0,
      "text": "Next door, in Sierra Leone, the Mende"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 277364.0,
      "end_time": 279363.0,
      "text": "also developed a syllabary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 279387.0,
      "end_time": 282995.0,
      "text": "but theirs reads from right to left."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 283190.0,
      "end_time": 286385.0,
      "text": "Africa has had a long tradition of design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 286409.0,
      "end_time": 290800.0,
      "text": "a well-defined design sensibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 290320.0,
      "end_time": 292310.0,
      "text": "but the problem in Africa has been that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 292334.0,
      "end_time": 295800.0,
      "text": "especially today, designers in Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 295320.0,
      "end_time": 297542.0,
      "text": "struggle with all forms of design"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 297566.0,
      "end_time": 302480.0,
      "text": "because they are more apt to look outward"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 302720.0,
      "end_time": 304676.0,
      "text": "for influence and inspiration."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 304700.0,
      "end_time": 308873.0,
      "text": "The creative spirit in Africa, the creative tradition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 308897.0,
      "end_time": 311748.0,
      "text": "is as potent as it has always been,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 311773.0,
      "end_time": 315796.0,
      "text": "if only designers could look within."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 315820.0,
      "end_time": 318687.0,
      "text": "This Ethiopic cross illustrates"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 318711.0,
      "end_time": 321467.0,
      "text": "what Dr. Ron Eglash has established:"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 321491.0,
      "end_time": 325356.0,
      "text": "that Africa has a lot to contribute to computing"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 325380.0,
      "end_time": 330732.0,
      "text": "and mathematics through their intuitive grasp of fractals."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 330756.0,
      "end_time": 334799.0,
      "text": "Africans of antiquity created civilization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 334823.0,
      "end_time": 338111.0,
      "text": "and their monuments, which still stand today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 338136.0,
      "end_time": 341696.0,
      "text": "are a true testimony of their greatness."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 341720.0,
      "end_time": 345614.0,
      "text": "Most probably, one of humanity&#39;s greatest achievements"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 345638.0,
      "end_time": 348580.0,
      "text": "is the invention of the alphabet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 348604.0,
      "end_time": 351698.0,
      "text": "and that has been attributed to Mesopotamia"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 351722.0,
      "end_time": 357263.0,
      "text": "with their invention of cuneiform in 1600 BC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 357287.0,
      "end_time": 361100.0,
      "text": "followed by hieroglyphics in Egypt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 361250.0,
      "end_time": 366469.0,
      "text": "and that story has been cast in stone as historical fact."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 366494.0,
      "end_time": 369184.0,
      "text": "That is, until 1998,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 369208.0,
      "end_time": 374303.0,
      "text": "when one Yale professor John Coleman Darnell"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 374327.0,
      "end_time": 377693.0,
      "text": "discovered these inscriptions in the Thebes desert"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 377717.0,
      "end_time": 381530.0,
      "text": "on the limestone cliffs in western Egypt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 381770.0,
      "end_time": 387289.0,
      "text": "and these have been dated at between 1800 and 1900 B.C.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 387313.0,
      "end_time": 390298.0,
      "text": "centuries before Mesopotamia."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 390322.0,
      "end_time": 393226.0,
      "text": "Called Wadi el-Hol"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 393250.0,
      "end_time": 396432.0,
      "text": "because of the place that they were discovered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 396456.0,
      "end_time": 399837.0,
      "text": "these inscriptions -- research is still going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 399861.0,
      "end_time": 402635.0,
      "text": "a few of them have been deciphered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 402659.0,
      "end_time": 405142.0,
      "text": "but there is consensus among scholars"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 405166.0,
      "end_time": 410359.0,
      "text": "that this is really humanity&#39;s first alphabet."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 410383.0,
      "end_time": 413402.0,
      "text": "Over here, you see a paleographic chart"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 413427.0,
      "end_time": 416520.0,
      "text": "that shows what has been deciphered so far,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 416544.0,
      "end_time": 419929.0,
      "text": "starting with the letter A, \"ālep,\" at the top,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 419953.0,
      "end_time": 423614.0,
      "text": "and \"bêt,\" in the middle, and so forth."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 423638.0,
      "end_time": 427227.0,
      "text": "It is time that students of design in Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 427251.0,
      "end_time": 431443.0,
      "text": "read the works of titans like Cheikh Anta Diop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 431468.0,
      "end_time": 433560.0,
      "text": "Senegal&#39;s Cheikh Anta Diop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 433584.0,
      "end_time": 436643.0,
      "text": "whose seminal work on Egypt is vindicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 436667.0,
      "end_time": 439775.0,
      "text": "by this discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 439800.0,
      "end_time": 442863.0,
      "text": "The last word goes to the great Jamaican leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 442887.0,
      "end_time": 444852.0,
      "text": "Marcus Mosiah Garvey"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 444876.0,
      "end_time": 448510.0,
      "text": "and the Akan people of Ghana"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 448760.0,
      "end_time": 450425.0,
      "text": "with their Adinkra symbol Sankofa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 450449.0,
      "end_time": 452667.0,
      "text": "which encourages us to go to the past"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 452691.0,
      "end_time": 454839.0,
      "text": "so as to inform our present"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 454863.0,
      "end_time": 459441.0,
      "text": "and build on a future for us and our children."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 459465.0,
      "end_time": 463681.0,
      "text": "It is also time that designers in Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 463706.0,
      "end_time": 466308.0,
      "text": "stop looking outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 466332.0,
      "end_time": 468698.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve been looking outward for a long time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 468722.0,
      "end_time": 471100.0,
      "text": "yet what they were looking for"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 471340.0,
      "end_time": 475962.0,
      "text": "has been right there within grasp, right within them."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 475987.0,
      "end_time": 477767.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
